{"type":null,"faqId":24784,"title":"系统运行缓慢，怎么办？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p6{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>您可以尝试以下方法：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <a name=\"gen-id1.11.5.2.2.1.1\"></a><span>当前运行的应用程序过多，请关闭一些暂时不用的应用程序。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<a name=\"gen-id1.11.5.2.2.1.2\"></a><span>在主屏幕上点击“设置 &gt; 应用程序管理 &gt; 正在运行”，点击当前不需要使用的应用程序，然后点击“停止”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<a name=\"gen-id1.11.5.2.2.1.3\"><a name=\"figd0e3022\"><a name=\"gen-id1.11.5.2.2.1.3.1.1\"></a></a></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=86213\" style=\"width:5.35625in;height:2.557639in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n <a name=\"gen-id1.11.5.2.2.2.1\"></a><span>安装的应用程序太多，系统盘空间不足，导致系统运行缓慢。可以卸载一些应用程序，释放系统盘空间。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<a name=\"gen-id1.11.5.2.2.2.2\"></a><a name=\"gen-id1.11.5.2.2.2.2\"></a><span>在主屏幕长按需要卸载的应用程序，并将其拖动至“</span><a name=\"gen-id1.11.5.2.2.2.2.1.1\"></a><a name=\"gen-id1.11.5.2.2.2.2.1.1\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=86214\" style=\"width:0.15416667in;height:0.11319444in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<a name=\"gen-id1.11.5.2.2.2.3\"><a name=\"figd0e3035\"><a name=\"gen-id1.11.5.2.2.2.3.1.1\"></a></a></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=86215\" style=\"width:1.6944444in;height:2.5597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n <a name=\"gen-id1.11.5.2.2.3.1\"></a><span>重启荣耀 X2，系统会自动关闭暂时不用的进程及应用程序。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<a name=\"gen-id1.11.5.2.3\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=86216\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span>所有图片仅供参考，具体操作请以实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":175,"faqType":"系统功能及设置","useful":1,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8784","faqTypeCode":"Tablet-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1430104345000,"seriesProductName":"GEM-703L","visitedTimes":218,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"系统运行,系统慢,卡,卡顿,不流畅","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}